Package seng202.group7.controllers.data

Class ControllerData

java.lang.Object
seng202.group7.controllers.data.ControllerData
public final class ControllerData
extends java.lang.Object
This class acts as a connection between the controllers passing data through here so that only the controller's initialization it can get the relevant data it needs. It accomplishes this by being a singleton class so only one instance of it can exist.
Author:
John Elliott, Jack McCorkindale
